<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Nexus 인증 번호</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" as="style" crossorigin href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard@v1.3.9/dist/web/static/pretendard.min.css" />
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        p {
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            word-break: keep-all;
        }
        body {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 24px;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            font-family: Pretendard, sans-serif;
        }
        .container {
            margin: 0 auto;
            max-width: 720px;
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 16px;
            background-color: #fff;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 24px 0;
            background-color: #171C24;
        }
        .article {
            width: 100%;
        }
        .textSection {
            padding: 16px 24px;
        }
        .textSection > p {
            color: #858585;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 20px;
            letter-spacing: -0.064px;
        }
        .numberSection {
            padding: 24px 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .title {
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            color: #0A0A0A;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            line-height: 32px;
            letter-spacing: -0.01px;
        }
        table {
            margin: 0 auto;
            border-spacing: 8px;
        }
        td {
            width: 52px;
            height: 64px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.12);
            background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.02);
            text-align: center;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }
        .number {
            color: #0A0A0A;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 600;
            line-height: 40px;
            letter-spacing: -0.051px;
            margin: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <img src="https://nexusbzcdn.blob.core.windows.net/container-1/nexusEmailLogo.png" alt="logo image">
    </div>
    <div class="article">
        <div class="textSection">
            <p>
안녕하세요, Nexus입니다.
아래 인증번호를 입력하여 이메일 인증을 완료해 주세요.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="numberSection">
            <div class="title">인증번호</div>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    {{#each code}}
                        <td><h1 class="number">{{this}}</h1></td>
                    {{/each}}
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
        <div class="textSection">
            <p>
이 인증번호는 보안상의 이유로 발송 후 10분간만 유효합니다.
회원님의 계정 보호를 위해 타인과 공유하지 마세요.

감사합니다.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
